eventDecorators.name: AddrChanged
eventDecorators.description: An event emitted when a vote has been cast on a proposal. Triggers on new deposit call.

eventDecorators.name: NameChanged
eventDecorators.description: An event emitted when a vote has been cast on a proposal. Triggers on new deposit call.

eventDecorators.name: OwnershipTransferred
eventDecorators.description: An event emitted when a vote has been cast on a proposal. Triggers on new deposit call.

functionDecorators.name: addr
functionDecorators.description: Gets the address associated to an ENS node.

returnDecorators.description: the address of the target node.

functionDecorators.name: name
functionDecorators.description: Gets the name associated to an ENS node.

returnDecorators.description: the name of the target ENS node.

functionDecorators.name: owner
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: renounceOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

functionDecorators.name: setAddr
functionDecorators.description: Lets the manager set the address associated with an ENS node.

functionDecorators.name: setName
functionDecorators.description: Lets the manager set the name associated with an ENS node.

functionDecorators.name: supportsInterface
functionDecorators.description: Returns true if the resolver implements the interface specified by the provided hash.

parameterDecorators.name: _interfaceID
parameterDecorators.description: The ID of the interface to check for.

returnDecorators.description: True if the contract implements the requested interface.

functionDecorators.name: transferOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
